  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b85\u0baa\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf.\u0b9a\u0bbf.\u0b9f\u0bbf.\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Army soldier assaulted and gun stolen incident - Inquiries to CCD",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "C.C.T. is investigating the assault of a policeman and an army soldier during the demonstration at the Pattaramullai-Poltuva junction from the entrance circle of the Parliament. have been handed over to the Colombo Crime Squad.",
        "While a complaint was registered at the Poralai Police Station regarding this incident, the Poralai, Welikadai Police had started investigations in the background of C.C.T. has been handed over to Colombo Crime Prevention Unit.",
        "Police Spokesman Senior Inspector Nihal Taltuwa said the investigations were transferred to the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit under the order of Western Province Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police Deshabandu Tennakone.",
        "On July 13, protesters took various steps to seize the Speaker's House and Parliament.",
        "During this, the army announced through a statement that the protestors had attacked two army soldiers and seized two Ri 56 rifles from them.",
        "However, in a statement issued by the police headquarters, an army officer and a police officer were seriously assaulted and injured and the soldier's duty rifle was confiscated and two magazines containing 60 bullets were confiscated along with the rifle.",
        "In this case, attention has also been paid to the incident in the cabinet meeting held last night and President Ranilwickramasinghe has directed the security officials to take any action to recover the confiscated gun."
      ],
